, rectify and delete data concerning them which may be exercised directly or via Personal Space by writing to:</p>\r\n<p>FROMAGERIES BEL SA.<br />\r\n16, Boulevard Malesherbes<br />\r\n75008 Paris</p>\r\n<p>· Security of your personal data:</p>\r\n<p>FROMAGERIES BEL agrees to comply with the provisions of the law "Informatique et Libertés" n ° 78-17 of 6 January 1978.</p>\r\n<p>FROMAGERIES BEL ensures optimal security measures against loss, misuse and alteration of the information entrusted to it by users. All data received on our website are backed up daily and stored on backup media.</p>\r\n<p>Cookies:</p>\r\n<p>FROMAGERIES BEL informs you that it may use "cookies" temporary valid time of a consultation session of the website "www.fondation-bel.org".</p>\r\n<p>These "Cookies" are data stored in RAM in your computer. They do not allow us to identify you, but it records information relating to your browsing our site (which pages you visited, the date and time of visit, etc..) We can read during your subsequent visits.</p>\r\n<p>The data collected through "cookies" are intended to identify you when you want to connect to your Career Center and remember your connection to the Internet site "www.fondation-bel.org".</p>\r\n<p>When you close your Internet browser, they are not saved.</p>\r\n<p>We inform you that you can oppose the registration of "cookies" by configuring your browser as follows:</p>\r\n<p>· If you browse the Internet with Internet Explorer 3 or 4 (Microsoft): Click "view", "options", "advanced". Among the different warnings you can activate, the fourth is entitled "warn before accepting cookies" and only on Internet Explorer 4, the fifth is entitled "always refuse cookies".</p>\r\n<p>· If you browse the Internet with Navigator Gold 3 (Netscape): Click "Options", "network preferences", "protocols". Among the different warnings you can activate, the first is "warn before accepting a cookie". You will be warned (e) upon the arrival of a "cookie" and you can prevent it from being stored by your browser</p>\r\n<p>· If you are using browser versions other than those mentioned, thank you to refer to the help files or manual.</p>\r\n<p>Applicable Law<br />\r\nThis site is subject to French law</p>\r\n<p>Various<br />\r\nFROMAGERIES BEL company is committed to making every effort to ensure users with accessibility at all times and to do its utmost to remedy promptly any downtime.<br />\r\nFROMAGERIES BEL company reserves the right to update these terms at any time without notice.</p>\r\n<!--:-->', '<!--:fr-->Mentions Légales<!--:--><!--:en-->Legals<!--:-->', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'mentions-legales', '', '', '2012-07-12 09:49:46', '2012-07-12 08:49:46', '', 0, 'http://fondation-bel.draft.lu/?page_id=88', 0, 'page', '', 0) ; 
