ectives peuvent générer de magnifiques succès. Notre Fondation renforce cette ambition en apportant sa pierre à la construction <strong>d’un monde qui doit permettre à chacun de grandir avec le sourire</strong>.<!--:-->&nbsp;<!--:en-->The group\'s mission is to bring the Fair to smile more and more families in the world, the pleasure afforded by its daily products, developed with the best milk. Given the special place of our brands on five continents, and in the relationship that links the generations around food, we wanted to extend our daily responsibility with a commitment to those who are both the weakest and holders of a world under construction. The foundation of Bel, founded in 2008 by the Bel Group and its shareholder Unibel, is all over the world for children and their welfare by promoting balanced eating habits and the environmental conservation, since it determines a healthy diet. The will of the Foundation is to give opportunities to a patchwork of bringing hope to the people who benefit. Instead of great achievements very ambitious, we have chosen to support the men and women whose ideas, courage, conviction and commitment are our examples to follow, perhaps, certainly welcome and support. We hope that our Foundation is the image of our company: a human adventure with a mission that our employees are proud and stakeholders. That\'s why we launched a program in 2010 to 10 annual scholarships to enable them to propose projects that are important to heart. Every day, sharing the enthusiasm and smile, Bel and colleagues believe that small group initiatives can generate tremendous success. Our Foundation supports this ambition while making its contribution to building a world that should enable everyone to grow up with a smile.\r\n\r\n<!--:-->', 'Oiseau-Lire', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '73-revision-7', '', '', '2012-07-11 16:28:47', '2012-07-11 15:28:47', '', 73, 'http://fondation-bel.draft.lu/73-revision-7/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ; 
